Privacy Policy for K-Utility

This privacy policy outlines how K-Utility collects, uses, and protects personal information obtained through the use of our Discord bot.

Information Collection and Use

When using K-Utility, we may collect personal information, such as your Discord username and ID, in order to provide language learning services and to improve our bot. We may also collect non-personal information, such as server usage statistics and other user interactions with the bot.

Use of Information

We use personal and non-personal information collected through the bot to provide language learning services and to improve our bot. We may also use the information to communicate with users, including sending messages or notifications about bot updates or new features.

Protection of Information

We take reasonable measures to protect the personal information we collect through the bot. We will not sell or otherwise distribute personal information collected through the bot to third parties unless required by law.

Data Retention

We retain personal information collected through the bot for as long as necessary to provide language learning services and to improve our bot.

Changes to this Privacy Policy

We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Users will be notified of any changes by posting the updated policy on our Discord server.

Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this privacy policy, please contact us at https://discord.gg/5gZ2eFTsZq.

By using K-Utility, you agree to the terms outlined in this privacy policy.
